nodes.text: "No-Nines" was the nickname of a Galactic Republic clone trooper living during the Clone Wars. A clone of the Human male bounty hunter Jango Fett, No-Nines was born on the planet Kamino, and stood 1.83 meters fully-grown. In 22 BBY, he served in the Mission to Kynachi with a group of clone troopers which earned the moniker of Breakout Squad.
No-Nines appears in Ryder Windham's young readers novel, The Clone Wars: Secret Missions 1: Breakout Squad.
